    "(3) To forecast an ML-based NIDS model on the basis of the outcomes of an adversary assault, the utility and challenges of identifying the underlying ML method are highlighted.",
    "This challenge stems from the diverse ML algorithms used in creating ML-based NIDSs.",
    "The use of DL has yielded excellent results in different areas.",
    "However, DL models face major difficulties in identification and protection against adversarial samples (AEs) [71].As indicated in the study by Meng et al. [110], the defense tactics covered are not exclusive of one another; a defense strategy may combine several ideas.",
